channel.title: Other People can't connect to my server
channel.description: I recently tried to create a server but, only I can connect to it thru 127.0.0.1 but not thru the actual server ip. Im not sure if I portforwarded right but I have a Linksys WRT54G2 router and I also have NO-IP DUC. If can help, please explain in detail if you have to. Im using a desktop running on Windows XP with a router connected. I followed all steps and I think it has to do with my router/ portforwarding. Thanks in advance.
